Package com.georgeludwigtech.highstock.components

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractHighStock
    This component is the base of any HighStock !! You can use it for all your charts, and define all the parameters by using the options parameters or by adding datas to the jquery object : $("#client").data("highstock", {...}); The Java and JavaScript JSON parameter will be merged during the initialization of the HighStock.
